thread.title: A quiet end to an eventful term for Fed Chair Yellen

title: A quiet end to an eventful term for Fed Chair Yellen
text:
A quiet end to an eventful term for Fed Chair Yellen Wednesday, January 31, 2018 - 01:34 
The Federal Reserve's latest policy meeting ended Wednesday, the last for outgoing Chair Janet Yellen. And though the economy may be humming along, a few wildcard factors have yet to play out - like President Trump's huge tax overhaul. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
